<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Kelińder Sábıge, adal júrekpen ҮРәж83</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
.  G         D     G      C   G/D
 Kelińder, Sábıge, adal júrekpen,
.D Em D   A/D       G  D/A  A D
 Kelińder Oǵan Betlehemge tezirek.
.Bm/Am/G Am G  D   G  Am   B
 Dúnıege keldi ǵalamnyń Patshasy.

[C1]
.       G
   Kelińder, taǵzym etińder,
.       G
   Kelińder, taǵzym etińder,
.       D7   G  D         G C G/D D7 G
   Kelińder, taǵzym etińder, Táńirge!

[V2]
 Jaryqtan máńgi jaryq,
 Qudaı týdy Qudaıdan,
 Pák qyzdan týdy Ol kishipeıil.
 Adam bop keldi jaralmaǵan Qudaı.

[V3]
 Isa, Saǵan kelemiz, Saǵan sıynamyz.
 Qurmettep, Seni madaqtap án aıtamyz.
 Máńgilik Sóz adam bop jerge keldi.</lyrics>
<key>G</key>
<author>Wade, John Francis (circa 1710-1786), Hillsong Worship</author>
